Departing the State Department

From:RossAJ@state.gov To: RossAJ@state.gov Date: 2013-03-11 14:14 Subject: Departing the State Department

Dear Friends & Colleagues: Tomorrow will be my last day as Senior Advisor for Innovation to the Secretary of State. It has been a remarkable and rewarding last four years. There are far too many people for me to thank for their support, but I did want to specifically extend my thanks to former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton
